  "title": "Software Engineer",
  "description": "<p>In this role, you will be responsible for writing and maintaining high-quality code for sofware applications. The ideal candidate will have experience in software development, a strong knowledge of programming languages, and the ability to work collaboratively with a team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Write clean, efficient, and well-documented code for software applications.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with other team members to design and implement new features.</li>\n  <li>Participate in code reviews to ensure code quality and adherence to coding standards.</li>\n  <li>Identify and troubleshoot software defects and issues.</li>\n  <li>Stay up-to-date with the latest software development trends and technologies.</li>\n  <li>Participate in team meetings and contribution to process improvement intiatives.</li>\n  <li>Ensure software applications and delivered on time and within scope.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
